An animated adventure for all ages, with original music and an all-star cast, Smallfoot turns a myth upside down when a bright young yeti finds something he thought didn’t exist—a human.  News of this “smallfoot” throws the simple yeti community into an uproar over what else might be out there in the big world beyond their snowy village, in an all new story about friendship, courage and the joy of discovery.  Channing Tatum as the yeti, Migo
James Corden as the Smallfoot, Percy
Zendaya as Meechee
Common as Stonekeeper
LeBron James as Gwangi
Danny DeVito as Dorgle Also starring: Gina Rodriguez, Yara Shahidi, Ely Henry, and Jimmy Tatro. Smallfoot is directed by Karey Kirkpatrick, Annie Award-winning director of “Over the Hedge” and Annie nominee for the screenplays for “Chicken Run” and “James and the Giant Peach.”   